616
00:40:31,004 --> 00:40:32,164
and go back.

617
00:40:34,844 --> 00:40:36,244
If I did that,

618
00:40:37,764 --> 00:40:39,084
my sister and her husband

619
00:40:40,444 --> 00:40:42,004
would go looking for me.

620
00:40:44,764 --> 00:40:47,044
Sister Liu's wedding would be disrupted.

621
00:40:49,444 --> 00:40:51,244
They've all been so good to me.

622
00:40:52,924 --> 00:40:54,324
I cannot do this.

623
00:40:57,792 --> 00:40:58,848
Yunyi.

624
00:41:01,444 --> 00:41:03,204
Your father is not by your side.

625
00:41:05,884 --> 00:41:06,912
From now on,

626
00:41:13,484 --> 00:41:15,204
